'Oh, Tuan Bholenath.'

00:16:31.080 --> 00:16:33.720
'Tolong bantu aku.
Beri aku kekuatan.'

00:16:34.040 --> 00:16:38.160
"Salam"

00:16:38.680 --> 00:16:44.640
"kepada Dewa Siwa."

00:17:30.160 --> 00:17:31.840
